handist.collections.function

Interface LongTBiFunction<T,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the object used as second parameter
    R - type of the return value

    public interface LongTBiFunction<T,R>
    Functional interface for actions taking a long and a generic type T as parameter and return type R.

    This interface removes the boxing and un-boxing operations that would otherwise occur when using the standard BiFunction with types Long and T as generic parameter types and T as the return type.
